### GET all tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/task HTTP/1.1

### GET task by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/task/ecedffb1-d215-11ed-b47d-00090ffe0001 HTTP/1.1

### GET task variables by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/task/ecedffb1-d215-11ed-b47d-00090ffe0001/variables HTTP/1.1
